➜国家网信办：1个月来处置违规“吃播”账号1.36万个
http://www.sohu.com/a/416141607_115479	39702
<div id="sohuplayer">
<script type="text/javascript" src="//tv.sohu.com/upload/swf/showVrsPlayer.js"></script>
